name: 56k
description:
As you try to upload an assignment for school, your connection doesn't work.

With the "help" of Clippy, go through a few levels, with assets and a general theme coming from windows 95.

This game was made for the 21st Godot Wild Jam in a week.

I only tested the windows and linux versions, so if you encouter any problems let me know.

I made the art, programming and sound fx, and the music comes from : https://finalgatestudios.itch.io/music-pack-1
